    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>croutons</strong> and <strong>cooked green beans</strong> to the bowl with the<strong> </strong>lettuce and toss all together – this is your <strong>Caesar salad</strong></p><p>Peel the <strong>cooled eggs</strong> and cut them in half</p>",
