      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Caesar salad</strong> in bowls topped with the <strong>egg halves, crunchy ciabatta pieces </strong>and <strong>Italian hard cheese shavings</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> Caesar dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
